Class MatrixMessageListFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • org.matrix.androidsdk.fragments.MatrixMessageListFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, MatrixMessagesFragment.MatrixMessagesListener

    public class MatrixMessageListFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements MatrixMessagesFragment.MatrixMessagesListener
    UI Fragment containing matrix messages for a given room. Contains MatrixMessagesFragment as a nested fragment to do the work.
